  <name>Pingveno</name>
  <summary>Look up Esperanto words</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Enjoy a complete offline dictionary right at your fingertips!</p>
    <p>Quickly search for words, explore translations, and browse definitions in a clean, distraction-free interface.</p>
    <p>With Reta Vortaro, you can easily update the dictionary to keep definitions fresh and accurate!</p>
    <p>No matter if you're just starting out or already fluent, this app is your perfect buddy for all things Esperanto!</p>
  </description>

